==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Officialism
<hw>Of*fi"cial*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of
being official; a system of official government; also, adherence to
office routine; red-tapism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Officialism</qex> may often drift into blunders.</q>
<rj><qau>Smiles.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Officiality</ent>⟦br⟧
